creator: MINMAXIA
descriptionHtml:
Can you conquer the Impossible Dungeon? (No - It's impossible)

This is an idle RPG where you build a party, unlock skills, buy upgrades, go up levels, and get more, all so that you can go deeper into the dungeon than ever before.

This game features a tournament system, lots of skill upgrades, quests, difficulty modes, character classes. Lots of fun!

There are NO popup ads in this game, There are NO banner ads. The only ads are reward videos that you can choose to watch if you want the offered bonus.
descriptionShort: This is an idle RPG where you see how deep into the dungeon you can go.

There are NO popup ads in this game, There are NO banner ads. The only ads are reward videos that you can choose to watch if you want the offered bonus.

This game features a tournament system, discord integration (claim roles directly from the game), lots of skill upgrades, quests, difficulty modes, character classes. Lots of fun!

This is an idle RPG where you build a party, unlock skills, buy upgrades, go up levels, and get more powerful, all so that you can go deeper into the dungeon than ever before.
descriptionShort: This is an idle RPG where you see how deep into the dungeon you can go.
